&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a highly experienced, dynamic and motivated person to share the role of leading the busy Wythenshawe Hospital outpatient cardiac rehabilitation service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have excellent interpersonal and communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have experience as an expert practitioner in the field of cardiac rehabilitation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have experience of a leadership role in an outpatient cardiac rehabilitation service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have experience leading a multi-disciplinary team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For this vacancy if you have not heard from us within 2 weeks from the closing date, please assume that you have not been successful on this occasion.&lt;/p&gt;
